1) A schedule - you need a way to display all medications and their scheduled doses.
2) Find next dose based on a date.
3) A way to mark a dose as given and specify the time it was given.
4) Time is problematic for medications given multiple times a day; consider time between doses and a method to calculate that.
5) Create a way to remind user to give a dose.

